sequenceDiagram
    participant Child
    participant UI as User Interface
    participant API as tRPC API
    participant SEC as Security Module
    participant DB as Database

    Note over Child,DB: Registration Flow
    
    Child->>UI: Enter username
    UI->>API: checkUsername(username)
    API->>DB: Query existing users
    DB-->>API: Username available
    API-->>UI: Validation result
    
    loop 4 Rounds
        UI->>API: getGridAnimals(count=25)
        API-->>UI: Return 25 random animals
        UI->>Child: Display 5×5 grid
        Child->>UI: Select favorite animal
        UI->>UI: Store selection
    end
    
    UI->>Child: Review 4 selected animals
    Child->>UI: Confirm password
    
    UI->>API: register(username, selections)
    API->>SEC: generateSalt()
    SEC-->>API: Random salt
    API->>SEC: hashPassword(selections, salt)
    SEC-->>API: Hashed password
    API->>DB: Store user + hashed password
    DB-->>API: Success
    API-->>UI: Registration complete
    UI->>Child: Success message 🎉

    Note over Child,DB: Login Flow
    
    Child->>UI: Enter username
    UI->>API: Verify username exists
    API->>DB: Check user
    DB-->>API: User found
    
    loop 4 Rounds
        UI->>API: getGridAnimals(count=25)
        API-->>UI: Return shuffled animals
        UI->>Child: Display randomized grid
        Child->>UI: Select animal
        UI->>UI: Store selection
    end
    
    UI->>API: login(username, selections)
    API->>DB: Get stored password + salt
    DB-->>API: Password data
    API->>SEC: verifyPassword(selections, stored)
    SEC-->>API: Match result
    
    alt Password matches
        API->>DB: Log successful attempt
        API->>DB: Reset failed attempts
        API-->>UI: Login success
        UI->>Child: Welcome back! 🎉
    else Password incorrect
        API->>DB: Increment failed attempts
        API->>DB: Check attempt count
        alt Attempts < 3
            API-->>UI: Wrong password, X tries left
            UI->>Child: Try again 😕
        else Attempts >= 3
            API->>DB: Lock account (5 min)
            API-->>UI: Account locked
            UI->>Child: Too many tries ⏰
        end
    end
